	<Summary>Brief Overview
One thousand years ago, Purgatori resided in Hell alongside the mighty Lucifer. Most of Hell's inhabitants protested her presence and one day that all this came to a climax when the Seven Deadly Sins used their powers to manipulate Hell's hordes, Lucifer AND Purgatori. This resulting in a series of events including Purgatori's slaughter of all the demons of Hell who dared challenge her, as well as Lucifer being overcome with an infatuation of Purgatori. He declares that he shall wed her and she accepts, always lusting for more power but on the night in which they are to sleep together instead she tries to drink of him and he becomes outraged, banishing her.</Summary>
